# Alphasound sshd config — overrides only what the OpenSSH defaults get
# wrong for our use case. Defaults already permit pubkey + password auth;
# we just need to allow password root login (default is prohibit-password).
# Password value comes from ALPHASOUND_ROOT_PASSWORD in alphasound.txt;
# leave that empty to lock the root account and force key-only auth.

PermitRootLogin yes
